      "name": "Should I adjust quantities for heavy eaters?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes! If you know your guest list includes hearty appetites, add 15-20% more food, especially for main proteins and starches."
      }
    },
    {
